SPELL NAME  : Mitra's Hand
SPELL SYNTAX: Mhand [<target>]
SPELL COST  : 50 SP
DESCRIPTION : Calls the hand of Mitra upon the target, or the cleric
              himself if no target is specified. Mitra rewards those
              who follow the path of good with protection and ability
              in combat. Evil creatures and people, however, experience
              condemnation and shame when Mitra's righteous hand is
              upon them, and become less able. Either way, the target
              is only affected for a short time.
